    systems gracefully.

    # Example

    ```nix
    cudaLib.utils.getRedistSystem true "aarch64-linux"
    => "linux-aarch64"
    ```

    ```nix
    cudaLib.utils.getRedistSystem false "aarch64-linux"
    => "linux-sbsa"
